## AST Node Types

<accordion>
  <item title="Document & Block Nodes">

| Node type        | Description                              | Key attrs                     |
|------------------|------------------------------------------|-------------------------------|
| `document`       | Root node                                | `meta`                        |
| `heading`        | `#` through `######`                     | `level`, `anchor`, `text`     |
| `paragraph`      | Prose paragraph                          | `children` (inline)           |
| `code_block`     | Fenced code block                        | `lang`, `title`, `highlight`  |
| `blockquote`     | `>` prefix                               | `children`                    |
| `list`           | Ordered or unordered                     | `ordered`, `tight`, `items`   |
| `list_item`      | Single list entry                        | `checked`, `children`         |
| `table`          | Markdown table                           | `align`, `head`, `rows`       |
| `horizontal_rule`| `---` separator                          | —                             |
| `html_block`     | Raw HTML pass-through                    | `raw`                         |

  </item>
  <item title="Zolto Tag Nodes">

| Node type    | Tag(s)                                   | Key attrs                          |
|--------------|------------------------------------------|------------------------------------|
| `callout`    | `<tip>` `<note>` `<warning>` etc.        | `variant`, `title`, `dismissable`  |
| `details`    | `<details>`                              | `summary`, `open`                  |
| `steps`      | `<steps>`                                | —                                  |
| `step`       | `<step>`                                 | `title`                            |
| `mcq`        | `<mcq>`                                  | `title`, `multiple`                |
| `mcq_option` | `<option>`                               | `correct`                          |
| `flashcard`  | `<flashcard>`                            | —                                  |
| `math`       | `<math>`                                 | `number`, `label`, `plot`          |
| `diagram`    | `<diagram>`                              | `type`, `title`                    |
| `chart`      | `<chart>`                                | `type`, `title`, `smooth`          |
| `card`       | `<card>`                                 | `title`, `href`, `variant`         |
| `cards`      | `<cards>`                                | `cols`                             |
| `tabs`       | `<tabs>`                                 | `variant`                          |
| `tab`        | `<tab>`                                  | `title`                            |
| `accordion`  | `<accordion>`                            | `exclusive`                        |
| `timeline`   | `<timeline>`                             | —                                  |
| `event`      | `<event>`                                | `date`, `title`                    |
| `gallery`    | `<gallery>`                              | `cols`, `caption`                  |
| `image`      | `<image>`                                | `src`, `alt`, `caption`            |
| `hero`       | `<hero>`                                 | `title`, `subtitle`, `align`       |
| `component`  | `<component>`                            | `name`, `props`                    |

  </item>
  <item title="Inline Nodes">

| Node type     | Source               | Key attrs             |
|---------------|----------------------|-----------------------|
| `text`        | Plain characters     | `value`               |
| `strong`      | `**…**`              | `children`            |
| `emphasis`    | `*…*`                | `children`            |
| `code_span`   | `` `…` ``            | `value`               |
| `strikethrough` | `~~…~~`            | `children`            |
| `link`        | `[…](…)`             | `href`, `title`       |
| `image_inline`| `![…](…)`            | `src`, `alt`          |
| `math_inline` | `<m>…</m>`           | `value`, `ast`        |
| `variable_ref`| `{name}`             | `name`, `resolved`    |
| `footnote_ref`| `[^ref]`             | `label`, `index`      |
| `hardbreak`   | `\` or 2+ spaces     | —                     |

  </item>
</accordion>

