## Diagnostic Object

```typescript
interface Diagnostic {
  message:  string;
  severity: 'error' | 'warning' | 'hint';
  code:     string;         // e.g. "E001", "W014"
  range: {
    start: { line: number; col: number; offset: number };
    end:   { line: number; col: number; offset: number };
  };
  source:   'parser' | 'validator' | 'transformer';
  fix?:     CodeFix;       // Optional auto-fix
}

interface CodeFix {
  description: string;
  edit: {
    offset: number;
    length: number;
    replacement: string;
  };
}
```

---

## Error Codes

<tabs>
  <tab title="Parser (P-)">

| Code  | Message                                  |
|-------|------------------------------------------|
| P001  | Unexpected end of input                  |
| P002  | Unclosed tag `<{name}>`                  |
| P003  | Mismatched closing tag `</{name}>`       |
| P004  | Invalid attribute syntax                 |
| P005  | Self-closing tag on a block element      |

  </tab>
  <tab title="Validator (V-)">

| Code  | Message                                          |
|-------|--------------------------------------------------|
| V001  | Unknown tag `<{name}>`                           |
| V002  | Required attribute `{attr}` missing on `<{tag}>` |
| V003  | Unknown attribute `{attr}` on `<{tag}>`          |
| V004  | `<slot>` used outside `<component>` definition   |
| V005  | Circular component reference: `{name}`           |
| V006  | Undefined variable reference: `{name}`           |
| V007  | Undefined equation label: `{label}`              |
| V008  | Duplicate heading anchor: `{anchor}`             |

  </tab>
  <tab title="Transformer (T-)">

| Code  | Message                                          |
|-------|--------------------------------------------------|
| T001  | KaTeX render error in `<math>`: {detail}         |
| T002  | MathJax fallback used (KaTeX unsupported macro)  |
| T003  | Component `{name}` redefined                     |
| T004  | Plot expression parse error: {expr}              |

  </tab>
</tabs>

